title: John Kerry, Ash Carter meeting with Australian counterparts
text:
> Top News John Kerry, Ash Carter meeting with Australian counterparts Secretary of State John Kerry walks with Australian Foreign Minister Julie Bishop at the Boston Marathon finish line, Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015, in Boston. Kerry and Secretary of Defense Ash Carter are meeting with their Australian counterparts in Boston to discuss security and trade issues.
